Easysoft Data Access is a suite of programs that add significant value to your investment in ODBC. With Easysoft software you can connect applications on more platforms to more database systems than ever before. The Easysoft ODBC-ODBC Bridge (OOB) enables ODBC calls to be made across the network from any Windows or Unix system to an ODBC data source running under Windows or Unix, permitting heterogeneous client-server operation and allowing client access to data wherever it is stored. Please note that if you want to connect to local data sources from a remote Java application, you will need the Easysoft JDBC-ODBC Bridge instead of this software. Chapter Guide • • • • Why ODBC? Driver Managers Why the Easysoft ODBC-ODBC Bridge? Where the Easysoft ODBC-ODBC Bridge fits in

